    <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap: 3rem; align-items: center;">
      <div>
        <p class="lead">MQ is the expression of Mauro Qashére’s lifelong pursuit of watchmaking excellence. Blending ancestral technique with modern design, MQ creates timepieces for those who value authenticity, refinement, and enduring prestige.</p>
        <p>With roots in European atelier traditions, Mauro established MQ to challenge the ordinary and craft watches that feel purposeful, rare, and unmistakably premium. Each collection is defined by subtle luxury, precise mechanics, and an uncompromising dedication to detail.</p>
        <p>MQ invites collectors and connoisseurs into a world where every dial, every finish, and every strap is chosen to elevate the art of wearing time.</p>
